<div class="sub-page">
    <section class="sub-hero" style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,51,102,0.8), rgba(0,51,102,0.9)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492144534655-ae79c964c9d7?q=80&w=2083') center/cover; padding: 100px 0;">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 style="color: white; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px;"><%= title %></h2>
            <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 18px;">KS 오토플랜과 함께하는 더 나은 카라이프</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section" style="padding: 100px 0;">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="background: white; padding: 60px; border-radius: 24px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); text-align: center;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px;"><%= title %> 페이지 준비 중</h3>
                <p style="color: #666; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 40px;">더욱 완성도 높은 정보를 제공하기 위해 페이지를 구축 중입니다.</p>
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary" style="display: inline-block;">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
